# Design bundle — the dashboard page (src/dashboard/page.rs) is GENERATED from
# .design-bundle/project/* via .design-bundle/gen_page.py, so those sources and
# the generator stay tracked. Ignore the heavyweight / non-build artifacts:
.design-bundle/chats/
.design-bundle/*_workflow.js
.design-bundle/project/screenshots/
.design-bundle/project/.thumbnail
